-- Monte Paschi says may need extra capital if extra loan charges needed 
-- 
-- Fri Jun 06, 2014 07:54AM EDT
-- None



ROME, June 6 (Reuters) - Banca Monte dei Paschi di Siena <BMPS.MI> warned on Friday it may need further capital strengthening measures if a ECB health check requires the Italian lender to book significant extra loan loss charges, according to the prospectus for its upcoming rights issue.

